1
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:26,840
Who are you?

2
00:00:27,160 --> 00:00:28,360
Why are you in my room?

3
00:00:31,080 --> 00:00:32,240
I'm just curious.

4
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:34,040
Why did you leave early?

5
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:36,320
What I do in my own home

6
00:00:36,320 --> 00:00:37,720
is none of your business.

7
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:50,740
You're my future sister-in-law.

8
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:54,920
How is it none of my business?

9
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:02,800
In that case,

10
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:05,290
you should learn some respect.

11
00:01:13,039 --> 00:01:15,760
A younger brother looking after what belongs to his older brother,

12
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,240
isn't that only right?

13
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:20,760
What do you think,

14
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:22,289
Sister-in-law?

15
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:42,800
Everyone,

16
00:01:43,759 --> 00:01:44,759
I, Mr. Yao,

17
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:46,560
have two things

18
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:48,240
to announce today.

19
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,800
The first thing is,

20
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:52,200
that the Yao family and the Song family

21
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:54,160
have reached an agreement

22
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:57,920
to jointly invest in and run a medicated soap factory.

23
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:02,200
And the second thing,

24
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,520
is a happy occasion.

25
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,600
This is also something Brother Song and I

26
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:07,160
decided together.

27
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,160
That is,

28
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:11,090
I will betroth my beloved daughter, Yao Shengsheng,

29
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:14,800
to the Song family's eldest son, Song Huainan.

30
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:17,880
The wedding ceremony is scheduled for next month.

31
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:23,600
Luoli.

32
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:25,720
I, Song Huainan, promise here,

33
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:28,720
that I will make you willing to marry me.

34
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,160
Marriage is a serious matter.

35
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:33,760
It concerns my lifelong happiness.

36
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,920
How could you decide without discussing it with me?

37
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:36,960
I'm not ready.

38
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:39,120
Nonsense.

39
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:42,810
Is this a business deal?

40
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:48,170
Shengsheng.

41
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:51,960
I, Song Huainan, promise here,

42
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:54,920
that I will make you willing to marry me.

43
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,079
Song Huainan.

44
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,560
This time,

45
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:02,200
I will turn your promises

46
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,880
into a dagger of vengeance

47
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:07,040
and thrust it deep into your heart.

48
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:15,720
I won't let anyone or anything

49
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:17,250
stand in the way of my plans.

50
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,040
Back then,

51
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,930
if I hadn't happened to pass by,

52
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:27,480
you would have met your end.

53
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,780
This wine tastes good.

54
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,660
How are things going on your side?

55
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:42,800
Open the door!

56
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,200
Open up! Yao Shengsheng!

57
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:45,380
W-What's going on?

58
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:46,560
Is he looking for you?

59
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,400
Open the door!

60
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,720
Is that person settled?

61
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:49,320
Of course.

62
00:03:51,920 --> 00:03:53,720
Detective Lin, I'm sorry.

63
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:54,960
What is it?

64
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:57,520
Yao Shengsheng!

65
00:03:58,240 --> 00:04:00,170
I have to inconvenience you today.

66
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:03,880
Wait, that's a huge inconvenience.

67
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:05,880
You don't expect me to go down from here? It's the third floor!

68
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:06,880
The man outside has a gun.

69
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:09,720
I'm afraid he'll misunderstand and the gun might go off.

70
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:10,920
Yao Shengsheng!

71
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:13,770
Open the door! Yao Shengsheng!

72
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:20,560
Master Song.

73
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,050
Is something wrong?

74
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,800
Where is the person who was in your room?

75
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:44,000
There's no one else in my room.

76
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,200
It's just me.

77
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,400
You are the Song family's daughter-in-law,

78
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:25,860
my future sister-in-law.

79
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:32,200
Don't let me catch you having an affair.

80
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:36,440
Or else I will...

81
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,240
You will what?

82
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:44,440
I won't let you off.

83
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:13,680
I'm curious.

84
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,160
Are you jealous?

85
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,040
Qingzhou.

86
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,520
You'd better behave yourself.

87
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:30,640
Don't play with fire.

88
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,650
Shengsheng.

89
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,240
Brother, look at him.

90
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,920
He accused me of meeting another man in secret,

91
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,720
and tried to ruin my reputation.

92
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:45,090
I'm warning you.

93
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:46,720
Stay away from my sister.

94
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,280
And,

95
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:50,159
don't slander her.

96
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:51,760
Let's go.

97
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:06,040
What game is she playing?

98
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:09,720
Does that punk

99
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,480
have feelings for you?

100
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:13,640
Brother, I'm tired today.

101
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,320
I don't want to talk about it.

102
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:14,880
Okay?

103
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,280
All right.

104
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,280
Whatever you say.

105
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:20,080
Go back to your room and rest.

106
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:20,800
Okay.

107
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,280
It seems

108
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:45,800
the Song brothers really like this face.

109
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,960
Next,

110
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,180
I will make the Song family

111
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:53,080
taste the bitterness of brothers turning against each other

112
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:54,840
and a household in chaos.

113
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:02,620
You must be Huainan's fiancée, Yao Shengsheng.

114
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:05,440
You certainly have the elegance of a well-bred lady.

115
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,160
It's a pity,

116
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:08,280
you came at a bad time.

117
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,640
Huainan had business early this morning,

118
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:11,440
so he went out.

119
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,210
When will he be back?

120
00:08:13,520 --> 00:08:14,440
I can wait for him.

121
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:15,520
That's hard to say.

122
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:17,760
Sometimes when Huainan goes out,

123
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,160
he doesn't return for days.

124
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,160
It doesn't matter.

125
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,400
I must see him today.

126
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:24,120
Then suit yourself.

127
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,250
Do you mind if I look around?

128
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:29,040
It's my first time at the Song residence.

129
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:29,440
You...

130
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:29,970
Madam...

131
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:32,760
The Young Master is taking a shower in the Eldest Young Master's room.
